    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将在一个名为 「CultureHouse」的住宅研究设施中生活 7 天，同时培育一种名为 &quot;吉尼欧 &quot;的神秘生命体，这个设施曾是一位失踪的生物化学家的居所。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras/411cff5f0b14c7867eb75d794c80dbfb.avif?t=1759894480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras_big/411cff5f0b14c7867eb75d794c80dbfb.avif?t=1759894480 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在培育吉尼欧的过程中，你会与「CultureHouse」的来访人物进行对话，并观察到周围发生的奇怪现象。随着时间推移，宁静的生活逐渐变得异常起来。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras/ff340a2abcb7d827874b311bd7b37ffe.avif?t=1759894480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras_big/ff340a2abcb7d827874b311bd7b37ffe.avif?t=1759894480 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >故事会以你的死亡（或世界末日）告终，并会从你访问「CultureHouse」的第一天早晨重新开始，吉尼欧的发展也会根据你的选择而呈现出与之前截然不同的形式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras/ae723ee2de5ead9f46f73a15f9b8ebe8.avif?t=1759894480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras_big/ae723ee2de5ead9f46f73a15f9b8ebe8.avif?t=1759894480 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在经历了几个灾难性的结局后，你将利用生化学家留下的笔记和与来访人物的对话中的线索，深入探究「CultureHouse」过去发生的悲惨事件，并揭示末日世界和吉尼欧之间的神秘联系。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras/2a21d58daba030500c07e1f9b754b55e.avif?t=1759894480\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2314460/extras_big/2a21d58daba030500c07e1f9b754b55e.avif?t=1759894480 width=800 height=450 /></span></p>",
